   <text>
      <body>

         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1659_dai_lns235ms_e_r.jpg"/>

         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>الله اکبر</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div1" corresp="#orig_div1">
            <p>God is great</p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation">
            <p>
               <stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
                  <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">نوازش خان</persName>
                      مُرید حضرت
                     <persName ref="#shahJahan">شاه جهان</persName>
                  </mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div2" corresp="#orig_div2">
            <p>
               <stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned>
                     <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">Nawazish Khan</persName>, disciple of Lord
                     <persName ref="#shahJahan">Shah Jahan</persName>
                  </mentioned></stamp>
            </p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p><lb/>زبده الاقران
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتم داس</persName>
                چودهری و
               <persName ref="#parasRam">پرسرام</persName>
                قانونگوی پرگنه <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
               <lb/>بعنایت امیدوار بوده بدانند عرضه داشتی که درینولا
               <lb/>ارسال داشته بودند بنظر در آمد و آنچه در باب دهات
               <lb/>نانکار خود معروض داشته بودند قبل ازین به شرافت پناه قاضی جیو
               <lb/>در حضور گفته شده در اینولا که ایشان در انجا میرسند آنچه
               <lb/>مقرر خواهند نمود منظور است باید که خاطر خود را
               <lb/>بهمه جهت جمع داشته در مالگذاری و آبادان کاری خود را
               <lb/>معاف و مقصر ندارند دراین باب تاکید
               <lb/>دانند تحریر فی التاریخ
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">
               <num>۳۰</num>
                ماه رجب سنه
               <num>۱۰۶۹</num>
               </date>
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div3" corresp="#orig_div3">
            <p><lb/>Eminent among Contemporaries
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> and
               <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qanungo">qanungo</ref> of <ref type="glossary"
                  target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>,
               <lb/>having hoped for kindness, know that the <ref type="glossary"
                  target="#gl_arzdasht">ʿarzdasht</ref> that had been
               <lb/>sent has come to [<persName ref="#nawazishKhan">Nawazish Khan's</persName>] attention. And whatever was represented about
               their <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_nankar">nankar</ref> 
               <lb/>villages previously had been said to
               the Refuge of Nobility <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qazi">Qazi</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Jiu</ref>
               <lb/>in the presence of the Lord. Now that he [<ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qazi">Qazi</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Jiu</ref>] has reached there, whatever
               <lb/>he shall decide is approved. It is necessary that [<persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName> and <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>]
               settle their minds
               <lb/>in every way and do not consider themselves excused or remiss in the collection
               of taxes and the work of populating [the area].
               <lb/>Know it to be confirmed in this matter. 
               <lb/>Written on the <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">30th of the month of
               Rajab in the year
               1069.</date>
               <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further</g>.
               <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further</g>.</p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="right margin">
            <p>هو</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div4" corresp="#orig_div4">
            <p>He [God] is</p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p><lb/>حسب المسطور مقرر دانسته بخاطر
               <lb/>جمع در خدمت مقید باشند بموجب قرار داد
               <lb/>و تحریر قاضی جیو منظور است
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_orig5" corresp="#orig_div5">
            <p><lb/>Knowing it to be appointed as written, [they should] be
               <lb/>engaged in service by settling [their] minds.
               <lb/>The writing and contract of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qazi">Qazi</ref>
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Jiu</ref> is approved.
               <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further</g>.
               <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further</g>.</p>
         </div>

         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1659_dai_lns235ms_e_v.jpg"/>

         <div xml:id="orig_div6" xml:lang="per" type="laterAddition" rend="top left">
            <p>نمبر
                 <num>۵</num>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div6" xml:id="trans_div6">
            <p>
               Number 5
            </p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div7" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="top right">
            <p>پروانه
               <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">نوازش خان</persName>
               دیهات نانکار</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div7" corresp="#orig_div7">
            <p><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">Parvana</ref> of
               <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">Nawazish Khan</persName>
               on the villages of
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_nankar">nankar</ref>. </p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div8" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="right margin">
            <p>بتاریخ
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">
                  <num>۳۰</num>
                   رجب سنه
                  <num>۱۰۶۹</num>
               </date>
                بدفتر دیوان رسید</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div8" corresp="#orig_div8">
            <p>Reached the office of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_diwan">diwan</ref> on
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">
                  <num>30</num>
                   Rajab in the year
                  <num>1069</num></date>.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
